Package: climenu
Title: Interactive Command-Line Menus for R
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R:
    person("Petr", "Čala", , "61505008@fsv.cuni.cz", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Petr Čala [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Petr Čala <61505008@fsv.cuni.cz>
Description: Provides interactive command-line menu functionality for R,
    inspired by popular CLI tools like inquirer.js, Python's pick, and Go's
    survey. Supports single and multiple selection menus with keyboard
    navigation (arrow keys or vi-style j/k), pre-selection, and graceful
    fallback for non-interactive environments. Designed to be lightweight
    and easy to integrate into R packages and scripts.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/PetrCala/climenu
BugReports: https://github.com/PetrCala/climenu/issues
